Package: MPAGE
Type: Package
Title: Module-based Pair-wise Analysis of Gene Expression
Version: 1.0.0
Description: Provides a complete workflow for analyzing RNA modification modules 
    and their dynamic changes across samples. It implements a module-based 
    pair-wise analysis of gene expression, integrating PPI network construction, 
    module identification, and various quantification methods for module activity 
    and gene pair relationships.
License: MIT
